    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EMBARK ON A MYTHIC SUDOKU ADVENTURE</h2>Awaken on a strange island with a mysterious temple, ridden with memorials of Avatars from a forgotten era. Explore the island, overcome the temple trials, and unlock the secrets of the past as you search for a way home.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A WHOLE NEW WAY TO SUDOKU</h2>It's more than just a grid: simultaneously solve multiple puzzles and uncover magical items that will help you along the way. Discover up to 9 themed sudoku variants, each with its own environment and a unique set of rules to match. With completely randomly generated puzzles, you'll get a new experience every time.<br><br><br>Plus, uncover additional modes as you complete trials:<br><strong>Duel Mode:</strong> Race against the AI as you solve the same grid and compete to see who can solve the most squares.<br><br><strong>Discovery Mode:</strong> Given an &quot;unsolvable&quot; puzzle, unlock &quot;discoveries&quot; which let YOU choose what clues to uncover to let you complete the puzzle.",
